description: Redevelopment of the site, comprising retention of the existing basement for provision of 35 car parking spaces and 75 cycle parking spaces, erection of 2 blocks ranging from 3 to 6 storeys in height to create 75 self contained flats comprising 14 x 1 bed, 50 x 2 bed and 11 x 3 bed units, together with landscaping and boundary treatments.
